{"Version":"4","Charset":"UTF-8","Variables":{"cookiepre":"B7Y9_2132_","auth":null,"saltkey":"TCC400zh","member_uid":"0","member_username":"","member_avatar":"https://avatar.saraba1st.com/data/avatar/000/00/00/00_avatar_small.jpg","groupid":"7","formhash":"e87d9b17","ismoderator":"0","readaccess":"20","notice":{"newpush":"0","newpm":"0","newprompt":"0","newmypost":"0"},"thread":{"tid":"1336553","fid":"6","posttableid":"0","typeid":"18","sortid":"0","readperm":"0","price":"0","author":"黄前久美子","authorid":"407355","subject":"『吹响吧！上低音号』专楼 剧场版上映中 3年生篇制作決定!","dateline":"1475209544","lastpost":"2020-1-20 10:57","lastposter":"老仓唯","views":"1352773","replies":"20150","displayorder":"0","highlight":"0","digest":"0","rate":"0","special":"0","attachment":"2","moderated":"1","closed":"0","stickreply":"0","recommends":"0","recommend_add":"0","recommend_sub":"0","heats":"3058","status":"3104","isgroup":"0","favtimes":"316","sharetimes":"0","stamp":"-1","icon":"-1","pushedaid":"0","cover":"0","replycredit":"0","relatebytag":"0","maxposition":"20450","bgcolor":"","comments":"0","hidden":"0","threadtable":"forum_thread","threadtableid":"0","posttable":"forum_post","addviews":"84","allreplies":"20150","is_archived":"","archiveid":"0","subjectenc":"%E3%80%8E%E5%90%B9%E5%93%8D%E5%90%A7%EF%BC%81%E4%B8%8A%E4%BD%8E%E9%9F%B3%E5%8F%B7%E3%80%8F%E4%B8%93%E6%A5%BC%20%E5%89%A7%E5%9C%BA%E7%89%88%E4%B8%8A%E6%98%A0%E4%B8%AD%203%E5%B9%B4%E7%94%9F%E7%AF%87%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A%21","short_subject":"『吹响吧！上低音号』专楼 剧场版上映中 3年生篇制作決 ...","replycredit_rule":{"extcreditstype":"5"},"recommendlevel":"0","heatlevel":"3","relay":"0","ordertype":"0","recommend":"0"},"fid":"6","postlist":[{"pid":"41384719","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"sorayang","authorid":"484072","dateline":"2018-10-26 09:24","message":"这两天无聊重新看TV版，刚好在第一季的中间过场不是有各个乐器吹标准音A么，正好最近也在练乐器就拿调音app来对了一下，结果发现动画里所有的标准音A都明显高了，京吹部室内排练是用单簧管来定音的，到了470Hz。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不过其实我不懂管弦乐团，有没有专业人士来说说，是乐团本来就这样、还是动画制作方面的考虑、或者单纯只是动画音频文件在传播过程中经过了某些不专业的调整导致的？","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"10043","username":"sorayang","adminid":"0","groupid":"49","memberstatus":"0","number":"9751","dbdateline":"1540517047","groupiconid":"9"},{"pid":"41385230","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"小白吃不明","authorid":"481845","dateline":"2018-10-26 10:11","message":"@asadako<br />\r\n<font color=\"#14171a\">誓いのフィナーレ公開まで半年を切ってた！</font><br />\r\n<font color=\"#14171a\"><br />\r\n</font><br />\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"https://img.saraba1st.com/forum/201810/26/101043sgzsasxzkuvtpgkv.jpg\" attach=\"41385230\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n吹吹小说的插图画家（<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"10044","username":"小白吃不明","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"9752","dbdateline":"1540519869","attachments":[],"imagelist":[],"groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"41385515","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"xwr","authorid":"179647","dateline":"2018-10-26 10:33","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41384719&amp;ptid=1336553\"><font color=\"#999999\">sorayang 发表于 2018-10-26 09:24</font></a><br />\r\n这两天无聊重新看TV版，刚好在第一季的中间过场不是有各个乐器吹标准音A么，正好最近也在练乐器就拿调音app ...</div><br />\n其实是吹的是 B-flat,466.16 hz吧，以前有专业人士指出过。第一季第十三集，调音吹的是B-flat，显示的也是B-flat，唯独显示的赫兹数是错误的442hz。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thoraxes.wordpress.com/2016/10/07/sound-euphonium-episode-13/\">https://thoraxes.wordpress.com/2016/10/07/sound-euphonium-episode-13/</a><br />\r<br />\r<br />\r<div class=\"reply_wrap\">One minor inconsistency here is that the tuner lists 442 hz. Depending on your part of the world, or if you’re in an orchestra or band (they also sometimes diverge depending on the conductor), some ensembles tune slightly sharper or flat than others. The standard used for bands in the US is A440 (the concert pitch A, at 440 hertz). 442 is not B-flat like the tuner indicates, it’s the pitch A but up two cents from what we usually use in the west (slightly sharper). B-flat is 466.16 hz. Even on a B-flat transposing instrument, it would still be the pitch B-natural. Usually basic tuners like that do not transpose, but some that do exist. <font color=\"Red\">The audio is correct that a B-flat is being played, and the B-flat note on the tuner is correct, but tuner has the wrong pitch for the hertz</font>. Bet you didn’t notice that!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/abload.de/img/sound_euphonium_box_3rpx5y.png\" /></div></div><div class=\"reply_wrap\">日本では、戦後の1948年に9年遅れでA = 440 Hzを導入したが、以前は、1859年のパリでの会議、1885年のウィーンでの会議で定められたA = 435 Hzを標準としていた。現在の日本ではオーケストラや演奏会用のピアノは A = 442〜443 Hzとなる場合が多い。</div><br />\n","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"10045","username":"xwr","adminid":"0","groupid":"57","memberstatus":"0","number":"9753","dbdateline":"1540521238","groupiconid":"12"},{"pid":"41385721","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"sorayang","authorid":"484072","dateline":"2018-10-26 10:50","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41385515&amp;ptid=1336553\"><font color=\"#999999\">xwr 发表于 2018-10-26 10:33</font></a><br />\r\n其实是吹的是 B-flat,466.16 hz吧，以前有专业人士指出过。第一季第十三集，调音吹的是B-flat，显示的也 ...</div><br />\n我不是看的剧中的调音器，而是安卓的调音app直接测播放出来的频率，所以不是很确定哪个环节的问题。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n的确看台词好像部长说的是降B，但如果降B的话那过场里的音明显又低了（我主要说的是前几集过场里展示每种乐器时候的音）","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"10046","username":"sorayang","adminid":"0","groupid":"49","memberstatus":"0","number":"9754","dbdateline":"1540522229","groupiconid":"9"},{"pid":"41385785","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"xwr","authorid":"179647","dateline":"2018-10-26 10:57","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41385721&amp;ptid=1336553\"><font color=\"#999999\">sorayang 发表于 2018-10-26 10:50</font></a><br />\r\n我不是看的剧中的调音器，而是安卓的调音app直接测播放出来的频率，所以不是很确定哪个环节的问题。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n的 ...</div><br />\n那就不知道了，也许可能是压片的问题？不知道如果直接播BD测试会怎么样。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"10047","username":"xwr","adminid":"0","groupid":"57","memberstatus":"0","number":"9755","dbdateline":"1540522671","groupiconid":"12"},{"pid":"41386166","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"xingenge","authorid":"425921","dateline":"2018-10-26 11:28","message":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/aleos696/status/1055661793337430018\">https://twitter.com/aleos696/status/1055661793337430018</a><br />\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"http://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/740ca5e5gy1fwlgqhnmu7j20l40xb0vv.jpg\" /></div><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n是那个学妹吧？","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"10048","username":"xingenge","adminid":"0","groupid":"53","memberstatus":"0","number":"9756","dbdateline":"1540524497","groupiconid":"11"},{"pid":"41386229","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"John.Zz.Li","authorid":"405212","dateline":"2018-10-26 11:34","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41386166&amp;ptid=1336553\"><font color=\"#999999\">xingenge 发表于 2018-10-26 11:28</font></a><br />\r\nhttps://twitter.com/aleos696/status/1055661793337430018</div><br />\n我死了。<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/079.png\" />","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"10049","username":"John.Zz.Li","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"9757","dbdateline":"1540524892","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"41387165","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"小白吃不明","authorid":"481845","dateline":"2018-10-26 13:04","message":"波乱的第二乐章贴吧有人继续翻译了，想看的人可以去看一下<br />\r\n啊，想看会动的奏啊，到底什么时候公布CV（","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","sta