ber":"9761","dbdateline":"1540538968","groupiconid":"10"},{"pid":"41389104","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"sorayang","authorid":"484072","dateline":"2018-10-26 15:45","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41387565&amp;ptid=1336553\"><font color=\"#999999\">cicsy 发表于 2018-10-26 13:43</font></a><br />\r\n比较奇怪的是乐团里好几首曲子都是以霙的双簧管展开，而双簧管是以几乎没法调音所以大家只能往他身上凑著 ...</div><br />\n第二季里双簧管的独奏其实很短，而且看到一种说法是现在的双簧管工艺已经能够保证音调准确稳定了，京吹部只有霙一个双簧水平又高出其他人，让她迁就其他人更简单吧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外我看走眼了，过场里演奏的的确是降B音，调音app里显示成了偏高的颜色，不过只稍微高了几赫兹完全在正常范围内。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"10054","username":"sorayang","adminid":"0","groupid":"49","memberstatus":"0","number":"9762","dbdateline":"1540539923","groupiconid":"9"},{"pid":"41389304","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"xingenge","authorid":"425921","dateline":"2018-10-26 16:01","message":"<a href=\"http://www.kyotoanimation.co.jp/shop/kitaujisuibu/\">http://www.kyotoanimation.co.jp/shop/kitaujisuibu/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"http://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/0068TvVBgy1fwlom5s193j30jg0jg459.jpg\" /></div><br />\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"http://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/0068TvVBgy1fwlom5q8e3j30jg0jgtc9.jpg\" /></div><br />\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"http://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/0068TvVBgy1fwlom5q8iyj30jg0jg43g.jpg\" /></div><br />\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"http://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/0068TvVBgy1fwlom5uahyj30z51dc7df.jpg\" /></div>","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"10055","username":"xingenge","adminid":"0","groupid":"53","memberstatus":"0","number":"9763","dbdateline":"1540540916","groupiconid":"11"},{"pid":"41389768","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"xwr","authorid":"179647","dateline":"2018-10-26 16:37","message":"<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/mw690/92b25e20gy1fwlouckk6tj20jg0jgwhr.jpg\" /></div