s":"0","number":"9767","dbdateline":"1540570048","groupiconid":"5"},{"pid":"41394350","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"adonai","authorid":"155630","dateline":"2018-10-27 00:31","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41386166&amp;ptid=1336553\"><font color=\"#999999\">xingenge 发表于 2018-10-26 11:28</font></a><br />\r\nhttps://twitter.com/aleos696/status/1055661793337430018</div><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/074.png\" />立华重制如果是这身就对了","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"10060","username":"adonai","adminid":"0","groupid":"52","memberstatus":"0","number":"9768","dbdateline":"1540571491","groupiconid":"10"},{"pid":"41396518","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"小白吃不明","authorid":"481845","dateline":"2018-10-27 10:31","message":"<font color=\"#333333\">Anime Trending采访牛尾憲輔 里面有一小段青鸟的预告，怕剧透不要点（</font><br />\r\n<font color=\"#333333\">https</font><font color=\"#333333\">://anitrendz</font><font color=\"#333333\">.net/news/2018/10/25/interview-liz-and-the-blue-bird-composer-kensuke-ushio/</font><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<font color=\"#333333\"><br />\r\n</font><br />\r\n<font color=\"#333333\"><br />\r\n</font><br />\r\n<font color=\"#333333\">一个简单的repo：</font><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<font color=\"#333333\">1.青鸟这部电影的工作是主题先行的，山田和牛尾先把主题聊透了才开始作曲工作</font><br />\r\n<font color=\"#333333\">2.牛尾认为这部电影讲了一个bittersweet的故事，虽然角色们是吹奏队员，但吹奏乐的元素可以完全从主题中剥离出来</font><br />\r\n<font color=\"#333333\">3.音乐在这部电影中是“润物细无声”的，不需要观众特别留意，但又把女孩子们完美地包裹起来</font><br />\r\n<font color=\"#333333\">4.牛尾认为自己在青鸟中的参与度比为其他影视作品供曲要高，其他作品曲子完成工作就结束，青鸟有一些工作是要和山田一起完成的</font><br />\r\n<font color=\"#333333\">5.青鸟中画面和音乐的精密配合是怎么做到的：山田先画分镜（应该也包括演出）→做出原画→牛尾看完原画开始作曲并收集其他音效（比如在中学教室的实景录音）→然后开始打（扯）磨（皮），必要的音乐影响了时间轴就改画，必要的画面影响了音乐就重新作曲</font><br />\r\n<font color=\"#333333\">6.青鸟中有很多轻盈空灵的声音是怎么做出来的：牛尾使用了“prepared piano”（预置钢琴），牛尾认为一群同龄的，碰巧住在很近的地方的孩子进了同一所学校一起念书这个过程本身就很“预置”，甚至有一些荒诞</font><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<font color=\"#333333\">预置钢琴，演奏者先將螺丝钉、乒乓球、橡皮、塑胶等物品预先夹置于钢琴的琴弦上，等到正式演奏时，琴槌便随机敲击到预置的材质，而发出不同的音响效果（随便搜来的解释</font><br />\r\n<font color=\"#333333\"><br />\r\n</font><br />\r\n","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"10061","username":"小白吃不明","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"9769","dbdateline":"1540607489","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"41396550","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"小白吃不明","authorid":"481845","dateline":"2018-10-27 10:34","message":"预置钢琴（<br />\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"https://img.saraba1st.com/forum/201810/27/103308t9y9g0lzzxiounru.jpg\" attach=\"41396550\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"https://img.saraba1st.com/forum/201810/27/103301htun2dttbb66sbpt.jpg\" attach=\"41396550\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"https://img.saraba1st.com/forum/201810/27/103316rpzhwowiw9jqmzoo.jpg\" attach=\"41396550\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n钢琴的预置和学校的“预置”，牛尾也是个有意思的人（<br />\r\n","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"10062","username":"小白吃不明","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"9770","dbdateline":"1540607649","attachments":[],"imagelist":[],"groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"41396589","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"小白吃不明","authorid":"481845","dateline":"2018-10-27 10:38","message":"连起来看<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/067.png\" /><br />\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"https://img.saraba1st.com/forum/201810/27/103731p67j74d7zjya3385.jpg\" attach=\"41396589\" /></div><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"https://img.saraba1st.com/forum/201810/27/103724dujl2uu12x86uu8j.jpg\" attach=\"41396589\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"10063","username":"小白吃不明","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0